Body-parameters:

Parameter Type Required Description

name

string

false

名字

sex

enum

false

性别
MALE
FEMALE

childrenIds

array

false

子女ID

  "name": "张三",
  "sex": "MALE",
  "childrenIds": [
    166
  ]
}

Response-fields:

Field Type Description Since

success

boolean

是否成功

-

message

string

错误提示(成功succeed)

-

data

object

处理成功返回的业务数据

-

code

string

错误代码

-

timestamp

string

响应时间

-

Response-example:

{
  "success": true,
  "message": "success",
  "data": {
    "waring": "You may have used non-display generics."
  },
  "code": "72177",
  "timestamp": "2021-08-23 23:03:45"
}

Curl-example:

curl -X POST -H 'Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8' -i http://localhost:8080/app/ --data '{

    166
  ]
}'

3.3. 分页查询订单信息

URL:  http://localhost:8080/app/page/{pageIndex}/{pageSize}

Type: GET

Author:  yu 2018/9/4.

Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded;charset=utf-8

Description:  分页查询订单信息

Path-parameters:

 Parameter Value Type Required Description

pageIndex

int32

true

当前页码

pageSize

int32

true

页面大小

Response-fields:

Field Type Description Since

records

array

分页数据

-

└─orderId

int32

订单id

-

└─orderType

enum

订单类型
WAIT_PAY -("0","已支付")
PAID -("1","已支付")
EXPIRED -("2","已经失效")

-

total

int64

获取总记录

-

size

int64

每页显示条数

-

count

int64

总数

-

page

int64

当前页码

-

Response-example:

{
  "records": [
    {
      "orderId": 395,
      "orderType": "WAIT_PAY"
    }
  ],
  "total": 967,
  "size": 471,
  "count": 415,
  "page": 780
}

Curl-example:

curl -X GET -i http://localhost:8080/app/page/315/10
